description: Dank Eats should rank high on your list of fusion pitas and fries to try. George, Bert, and James together concocted a brilliant mission to serve the good people of Richmond with good food and a side of good vibes. Now RVA is home to this dank green machine, and it’s flinging out the finest cuisine.Their eclectic selection of pita couldn’t be neata’. You’ve got the Chipotle Chicken Bacon Ranch with sweetly smoked applewood bacon, tangy chipotle ranch, and the house chicken, marinated in tasty thai basil. You’ve got the Classic Gyro, complete with Papa G’s famous tzatziki. If all this is Jamaican you hungry, you can always order the Reggae, mon! Kick back with this beautiful blend of spicy pickled jicama slaw, chipotle ranch, and cilantro lime aioli. Indulge in a special prize of curry, sweet potato, or bacon cheese fries. With this magnificent menu, you’ll be thankful when your tummy is dankful!
name: Dank Eats
